From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jorge Javier Araya Navarro <jorge@esavara.cr>
Date: Thu, 4 Sep 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Fix is_zenny_position: replace undeclared 'buffer' with
 default string

The function is_zenny_position in both src/utils.c and src/jputils.c
references 'buffer' which is declared in a different function
(is_position) and is not in scope. All switch cases already return
directly, so this is dead code. Replace with a safe default return
value.

---
 src/jputils.c | 2 +-
 src/utils.c   | 2 +-
 2 files changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/src/jputils.c b/src/jputils.c
index 77daf16..4fccb89 100644
--- a/src/jputils.c
+++ b/src/jputils.c
@@ -162,7 +162,7 @@ char *is_zenny_position(byte a)
             return "[ZENNY BOTTOML]";
     }

-    return buffer;
+    return "";
 }

 char *is_symbol(byte a)
diff --git a/src/utils.c b/src/utils.c
index 37f8495..d890c95 100644
--- a/src/utils.c
+++ b/src/utils.c
@@ -154,7 +154,7 @@ char *is_zenny_position(byte a)
             return "[ZENNY BOTTOML]";
     }

-    return buffer;
+    return "";
 }

 char *is_symbol(byte a)
--
2.48.1
